3𝓓 𝓦𝓲𝓷𝓷𝓲𝓮 𝓽𝓱𝓮 𝓟𝓸𝓸𝓱 𝓒𝓱𝓲𝓯𝓯𝓸𝓷 𝓒𝓪𝓴𝓮. 🍯 ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
We can still celebrate birthday during this circuit breaker period. The birthday girl was so surprised when the cake was delivered to her. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Everyone was already getting ready to sing birthday song to her via video conferencing! (Swipe to see the picture from client) ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Cake made entirely with chiffon sponge using freshly squeezed orange juice. ⁣

Do you love Ah Pooh bear? ⁣
⁣
